Package: arci
Title: Anderson-Rubin Confidence Intervals for IV Regression in R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Bas", "Machielsen", , "a.h.machielsen@uu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package constructs Anderson-Rubin confidence intervals for instrumental variable regression models in R using the `fixest` package. It provides functions to compute the intervals, plot them, and summarize the results.
